text: Huic vero terre ad acent prate ubi dicitur hreodham. In IIII locis. In uno loco XVII agroson eastan clifwara gemære.
And on norðan,et in alio loco XII agros.
On eastan is culinga gemære & on suðan clifwara gemære.
And on norðan,et in tertio loco VII agrosbe eastan.
And be westan & be norðan is clifwara gemereet in quarto loco sex agros.
And be suðan is culinga gemære.
And be westan is & be norðan clifwara gemære.
